<div class="content-box">
    <h1>Project Lifecycle</h1>
    <p>Every project in the Web Everything ecosystem moves through a rigorous maturation process. This guide explains what you can expect from each stage.</p>

    <div class="lifecycle-stages">
        <div class="stage-card">
            <div class="stage-header">
                <h2>Concept</h2>
                <span class="stage-percent">10%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-meter status-concept">
                <div class="meter-track"><div class="meter-fill"></div></div>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> Research & Design</p>
            <p>The problem space is being defined. No concrete implementation exists yet. We are gathering requirements and sketching APIs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="stage-card">
            <div class="stage-header">
                <h2>POC (Proof of Concept)</h2>
                <span class="stage-percent">30%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-meter status-poc">
                <div class="meter-track"><div class="meter-fill"></div></div>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> Experimental Code</p>
            <p>A rough implementation exists to prove the solution is viable. The API is volatile and likely to break. Do not use in production.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="stage-card">
            <div class="stage-header">
                <h2>Draft</h2>
                <span class="stage-percent">50%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-meter status-draft">
                <div class="meter-track"><div class="meter-fill"></div></div>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> Feature Development</p>
            <p>The core features are built, but API details are still being refined. Feedback helps shape the final specification.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="stage-card">
            <div class="stage-header">
                <h2>Candidate</h2>
                <span class="stage-percent">80%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-meter status-candidate">
                <div class="meter-track"><div class="meter-fill"></div></div>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> Testing & Validation</p>
            <p>Feature complete. The API is frozen. Focus is on conformance tests, browser compatibility, and documentation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="stage-card">
            <div class="stage-header">
                <h2>Stable</h2>
                <span class="stage-percent">100%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-meter status-stable">
                <div class="meter-track"><div class="meter-fill"></div></div>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> Production Ready</p>
            <p>The project follows Semantic Versioning. API is locked. Improvements are additive. Safe for mission-critical use.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

